test the time it takes to index and search random data.

- linux: `sudo apt-get install libmlpack-dev libboost-serialization-dev`
- macOS: `brew install mlpack`
- windows: `?`

> 16 GB 1867 MHz DDR3
> macOS 10.14.6 Mojave
